{"tid":1812804,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[Retweet] 致世界：關於中國肺炎，請勿相信資訊流通可以抵銷中國嘅消息封鎖系統","createTime":"2020-01-05T18:45:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-08T04:38:07.000Z","uid":236171,"like":72,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"347f55db361b04f3bc89231a9f112f3e5ae62ee6","tid":1812804,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T18:45:38.000Z","msg":"寫咗篇文，希望大家可以傳開佢。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/pentanov/status/1213890313124634625?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpentanov%2Fstatus%2F1213890313124634625%3Fs%3D19&d=4MF4O%2Bfy8eJNXT4C%2FvKi1WWzMblEAwKPRhfqpO9yGDY%3D&h=1c9ee0a3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpentanov%2Fstatus%2F1213890313124634625%3Fs%3D19&h=5355b413\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/pentanov/status/1213890313124634625?s=19</a><br />\n<br />\n我要全世界知道<br />\n1. 中國嘅消息封鎖對全世界每個人影響好大<br />\n2. 預防中國肺炎。情況俾你想像中差。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">TLDR:</span><br />\n中國可以喺上海呢個國際大都市直播一個假嘅倒數活動出嚟，全世界用咗三日時間先發現。<br />\n<br />\n所以唔好以為現今嘅資訊流通就代表你可以掌握中國境內情況。支共要封鎖消息輕而易舉。<br />\n<br />\n所有人請自己&amp;要求政府做好所有衛生措施。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全文</span></strong><br />\n<br />\nMy friends from around the world,<br />\n<br />\nDo NOT assume that the efficiency of modern information dissemination can make up for #Chinazi's censorship and deceit. <br />\n<br />\nAnd it doesn't matter where you live in. You will eventually be affected. By #ChinesePneumonia for one. <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#China faked the entire world into believing that they held a NYE countdown drone show in #Shanghai on live, when there wasn't even a countdown event in the area at all to begin with.<br />\n<br />\nThey weren't even trying hard to cover the lie and it took the free world THREE DAYS to realize the easily verifiable truth.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNow consider #CCP deliberately covering up an entire could-be epidemic - the #ChinesePneumonia.<br />\n<br />\nAccording to &quot;official&quot; records, 59 cases in #Wuhan, 16 in #HongKong, ZERO in the rest of #China. And according to interviews with Chinese tourists, most did not even know the existence, let alone the seriousness, of the disease.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNow think about the no. of Chinese people travelling around the world EVERY DAY. If one of them catches the disease, they won't know it. You won't know it. <br />\n<br />\nAnd by the time you realize, your country may have become an epidemic zone. <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSo for the sake of yourself and everyone else, please:<br />\n<br />\n1. Tell your gov to strengthen quarantine measure at the border <br />\n<br />\n2. Avoid travelling to China. If you have to, take ALL hygienic precautions possible. <br />\n<br />\n3.  For workers in ports of entry, wear a mask, wash your hands, and look out for people who looks unwell.<br />\n<br />\nGod bless the free world."},{"pid":"f59799f32af881e7fee098db26abd193d68c7b02","tid":1812804,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T18:47:36.000Z","msg":"我知而家好夜"},{"pid":"8804fea6e253d9acb20d96844f9b396845517f98","tid":1812804,"uid":263944,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T18:48:36.000Z","msg":"空氣推"},{"pid":"a07101ab55153f3fe4adfacc59fe4294c8ff2d67","tid":1812804,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f59799f32af881e7fee098db26abd193d68c7b02","tid":1812804,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T18:47:36.000Z","msg":"我知而家好夜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T18:49:11.000Z","msg":"但係未瞓嘅手足希望你哋幫手推"},{"pid":"bb029872b5a6439af8d9d63def9c8b4681139ecc","tid":1812804,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8804fea6e253d9ac