epidemic - the #ChinesePneumonia.<br />\n<br />\nAccording to &quot;official&quot; records, 59 cases in #Wuhan, 16 in #HongKong, ZERO in the rest of #China. And according to interviews with Chinese tourists, most did not even know the existence, let alone the seriousness, of the disease.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nNow think about the no. of Chinese people travelling around the world EVERY DAY. If one of them catches the disease, they won't know it. You won't know it. <br />\n<br />\nAnd by the time you realize, your country may have become an epidemic zone. <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSo for the sake of yourself and everyone else, please:<br />\n<br />\n1. Tell your gov to strengthen quarantine measure at the border <br />\n<br />\n2. Avoid travelling to China. If you have to, take ALL hygienic precautions possible. <br />\n<br />\n3.  For workers in ports of entry, wear a mask, wash your hands, and look out for people who looks unwell.<br />\n<br />\nGod bless the free world."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T19:02:06.000Z","msg":"應該開係world"},{"pid":"78b7b503baab711f3b949e6f3102d084b1a85721","tid":1812804,"uid":236171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"535820ce950f2e4b90c63f172fde034f3bf7aaf5","tid":1812804,"uid":236171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5a065d6b5511f7fc4301caa9399baec976bff122","tid":1812804,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7930b5d8db1fae03513cd4c910cdc3674dad7210","tid":1812804,"uid":236171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T18:52:45.000Z","msg":"支共嘅自私可以禍害全世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T18:59:00.000Z","msg":"我嘅願望好簡單<br />\n<br />\n我希望呢個 tweet 可以警惕到其他地方嘅人同政府，等佢哋及早做好相應嘅預防措施<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T18:59:55.000Z","msg":"救到幾多人得幾多人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T19: